Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.97,0:00:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是太阳系的明星秀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It is the show-stopper of our Solar System,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪亮的外表吸引着大量的爱好者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}basking in its own glow, it seduces all admirers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 美丽外表下隐藏着恶魔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}However, it is a beauty with a mean streak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星是一个环绕着冰质光环的气态星球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a massive, frigid ball of gas,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光环以40000英里每小时(64000千米每小时)旋转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}surrounded by icy rings hurdling at 40,000 miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星有着非常疯狂的气象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It is a planet of violent weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极地的飓风面积比美国还大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with a polar storm bigger than the United States of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星的一些气象是太阳系中最强大的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Saturn has some of the most powerful weather in the Solar System.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪电的能量比地球上的大100万倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The lightning could be a million times more powerful than here on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过土星的卫星更吸引人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But its moons are even more exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩克拉多斯(土卫二)上的喷泉 喷出几百英里高的水汽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The geysers on Enceladus are erupting water vapour hundreds of miles into the air
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里引力很小 且没有大气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because there's much lower gravity there and the fact that there's no atmosphere holding them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一颗土星卫星有大气 海洋和山脉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Another has an atmosphere with oceans and mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许某颗卫星上会有生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Could life exist on one of these moons?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星 光环王者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Saturn: Lord of the Rings.
